          <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white">WHO AM I?</h2>
          <p class="text-white font-light">
            - 14 years old <br />
            - "I use Arch btw" <br />
            - I like math, Physics, Programming and Design <br />
            - i play mostly minecraft and factorio
          </p>
        </div>
        <Social />
      </section>
      <div
        class="basis-[500px] lg:basis-[1300px] grow dark:bg-purple-800 pt-4 md:pt-16 flex flex-col"
